### GaadiX User Service API Tests
### Use this file in STS: Right-click → Run As → HTTP Request

### 1. Register New User
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "john@gaadix.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "phone": "9876543210"
}

###

### 2. Register Admin User
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Admin",
  "lastName": "User",
  "email": "admin@gaadix.com",
  "password": "admin123",
  "phone": "9876543211",
  "roles": ["ADMIN"]
}

###

### 3. Login User
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@gaadix.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### 4. Login Admin
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@gaadix.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

###

### 5. Get User by ID (Replace YOUR_TOKEN with accessToken from login)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/users/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

###

### 6. Get User by Email
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/users/email/john@gaadix.com
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

###

### 7. Get All Users (Admin Only)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/users
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN

###

### 8. Update User
PUT http://localhost:8081/api/v1/users/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "phone": "9876543210"
}

###

### 9. Refresh Token (Replace YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/auth/refresh?refreshToken=YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN

###

### 10. Logout
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

###

### Test Error Scenarios

### 11. Duplicate Email (Should Fail)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Jane",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "john@gaadix.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "phone": "9876543212"
}

###

### 12. Invalid Login (Should Fail)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@gaadix.com",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

###

### 13. Access Without Token (Should Fail)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/users/1

###

### 14. Invalid Token (Should Fail)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/users/1
Authorization: Bearer invalid_token_here

###

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8081/actuator/health

###
